		*    o A cheque or postal order for Ł5	   *
		*      payable to 'Graeme Blenkinsopp'.	   *
		*    o OR Ł5 UK Sterling (if not in UK).   *
		*    o OR Ł5 cash (by registered post)     *
		*					   *
		********************************************

Send To : Graeme Blenkinsopp, Movie Maker 2 Registration, 1 Oakley Green,
	  West Auckland, Bishop Auckland, County Durham. DL14 9JD. England.

NB: If any of the above items have not been included I may be reluctant
to send you a copy or it may be severely delayed.  I will not be held
resposible if one of your disks has a read/write error on it.  I will
assume you have formatted them.  I will not be held responsible for any
cash/letters/orders lost in the post.  On each registered copy, the name 
