Please also ensure you have sufficient postage on the SAE you provide.
If you are sending from another country (i.e. outside UK) then you MUST
provide enough postage or additional money to cover postage.  Anyone
within the UK must provide postage in stamps (not additional money).
The reason for this is simple, it ensures an extremely fast return.
If I only have to copy the disks and put them in a postbox, I can send
the package the same day I receive the order.  If you send a cheque,
there may be a delay until the cheque clears.
