To : Graeme Blenkinsopp, 1 Oakley Green, West Auckland, Bishop Auckland,
     County Durham.  DL14 9JD.  England.
@EndNode



@Node "Chapter5B" "Dave And The Chicken"
			   Dave And The Chicken
			   ====================

A small demo about a sprite with a big-nose and his strange exploits
with a chicken.  One day he finds a chicken running about in his
back-yard and chases after it.  This demo is about what happened next.
Various other dodgy characters join in the chase and all meet with some
untimely death or other.

The demo features digitised animations, 64-colour animated sprites,
'colourful' backdrops and excellent soundtracks.  It can be obtained
from Moslty Harmless BBS : (+44 1705 614 824).  The files are called
'DAVE1.LZX' and 'DAVE2.LZX'.

Or you can obtain the demo directly from me : Send :

