@Node "Chapter5C" "Fictional Rave Music Demo"
			 Fictional Rave Music Demo
			 =========================

Features seven of the best soundtracks I've ever written.  They are all
in an un-altered OctaMED state so you can load them directly into any
version of OctaMED.  Provided with the tracks is a user interface
program so you can listen to them without loading them individually
into OctaMED.  It features science fiction tracks, rave tracks, mellow
tracks and hardcore tracks.  Even if you don't like the tracks, you
can always use the samples in your own tracks.

The archive is 1MB and should be available from Moslty Harmless BBS :
(+44 1705 614 824).  The file is called 'FICTRAVE.LZX'.  The version
is designed to run from Hard Disk but I am currently working on
installer scripts to install to floppy as well.

