@Node "Chapter6B" "Bugs"
				   Bugs
				   ====

If you find any major bugs or incompatabilities, let me know about them.
The only other bug I know of is a fault of AMOS Professional.

The music is temporarily interrupted when loading a digitised image of an
actor or actress.  I had to write the interruption since AMOS Pro kept
turning the music off altogether if I just loaded and unpacked a screen
without stopping the music first.

@EndNode
